{#
    RKN Premium brand tokens
    ========================
    Fixed identity palette for the RKN Premium Theme — independent of the
    merchant's Salla color picker but overridable via the "RKN Premium"
    color preset in Theme Settings.

    Consumed by `assets/styles/home/*` and storefront header/footer via:
      - `--rkn-primary`   #004956  deep teal
      - `--rkn-secondary` #06c2b7  bright aqua
      - `--rkn-accent`    #ff9f1a  promotional orange
      - `--rkn-bg`        #f7f8fa  page canvas
#}
<style>
    :root {
        --rkn-primary: #004956;
        --rkn-primary-dark: #003640;
        --rkn-primary-light: #d9f0f2;
        --rkn-secondary: #06c2b7;
        --rkn-secondary-dark: #049e95;
        --rkn-secondary-light: #d4f7f4;
        --rkn-accent: #ff9f1a;
        --rkn-accent-dark: #e08600;
        --rkn-bg: #f7f8fa;
    }
</style>
